http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9913980463346544, \"rank\": 0.008268537555949572, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight faults\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One major surprise came for defending Olympic champions Sweden, which had kicked off with two clears but finished today in eighth place on 17 faults, afterPeder Fredricsonand Catch Me not S had an uncharacteristic run-out at the wall at fence 11 as well as a pole, notching up nine time-faults.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1005, \"end\": 1011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9883590078541971, \"rank\": 0.010396972920392263, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One major surprise\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"two clears\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1049}, {\"ngram\": \"eighth place\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"17 faults\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"afterPeder Fredricsonand Catch\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"an uncharacteristic run-out\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1182}, {\"ngram\": \"fence\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1191}, {\"ngram\": \"a pole\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"nine time-faults\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was very good until the wall and I do not really know, maybe I turned a little bit tight to it,\\\" Peder said.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"Peder\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then he got a bit surprised and did not know if he was supposed to jump it or what it was, so he stopped.\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that really surprised me because I had a very good feeling until then.\\\"\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very good feeling\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peder said that in thisnew format, with no drop score,he felt the pressure to get home.\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peder\", \"from\": 1546, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"thisnew format\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"no drop score\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1628, \"to\": 1632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Although I wasn't very worried because normally he does not stop,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But anyway, I had to make sure it did not happen again, but we were lucky.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We made it to the final and then we start on zero tomorrow.\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So for the sake of the results, it does not really matter.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sake\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But of course, I would have been happy with a clear.\\\"\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1920}, {\"ngram\": \"a clear\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Israel and Mexico complete the top 10 through to tomorrow but Switzerland provided another shock; having finished fifth as a team in Tokyo, they will not feature in tomorrow's final as they finished 12th today on a total of 24 faults.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1962, \"end\": 1968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9604537244013928, \"rank\": 0.041159299844265605, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1973, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999092470078457, \"rank\": 9.02655552850866e-05, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2024, \"end\": 2035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"score\": 0.9958431906598887, \"rank\": 0.003501198709709984, \"text\": \"Switzerland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Switzerland\"}, {\"begin\": 2095, \"end\": 2100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999245627920504, \"rank\": 5.317797763250496e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tomorrow\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2019}, {\"ngram\": \"another shock\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2058}, {\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2091}, {\"ngram\": \"a total\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2182}, {\"ngram\": \"24 faults\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Martin Fuchs, whose four-fault round with Leone Jei was not enough following Steve Guerdat and Dynamix De Belheme's eight and Pius Schwizer and Vancouver De Lanlore's 12, said it was \\\"definitely not the day we wished for\\\".\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9999999941546776, \"rank\": 5.845372361635749e-09, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}, {\"begin\": 2275, \"end\": 2288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Guerdat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steve Guerdat\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Guerdat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Guerdat\"}, {\"begin\": 2293, \"end\": 2300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dynamix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3158944870012568e-18, \"text\": \"Dynamix\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dynamix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dynamix\"}, {\"begin\": 2324, \"end\": 2337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pius_Schwizer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pius Schwizer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pius_Schwizer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pius_Schwizer\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whose four-fault round\", \"from\": 2212, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"Leone Jei\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"Vancouver De Lanlore\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2362}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I actually was very confident going in, believing that if it was a clear round we'd qualify for the final,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a clear round\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I was highly motivated and Leone Jei felt felt great throughout the course; I really believed that we could deliver this clear round and try to save our chances for the final.\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Leone Jei\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2580}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"this clear round\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"our chances\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe I was almost a bit too confident in the combination when he jumped the planks [at 13b] so well.\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the combination\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"the planks\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2803}, {\"ngram\": \"13b\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not focus enough for the c [element]; I was already thinking about bringing it home and not about jumping the fence first.\\\"\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the c\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"the fence\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You might also be interested in: Stay in touch with all the news in the run-up to and throughout the major shows and events during 2025 and beyond with a Horse & Hound subscription.Subscribe todayfor all you need to know ahead of these major events, plus online reports on the action as it happens from our expert team of reporters and in-depth analysis in our special commemorative magazines.\", \"from\": 2953, \"to\": 3359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3120, \"end\": 3133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Horse_&_Hound\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Horse & Hound\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"htt